        <para>
          <text>Under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><intref href="DLM193363">section 88</intref></citation>, the Crown acknowledges the statement by Ngati Ruanui of the cultural, spiritual, historical, and traditional association of Ngati Ruanui with the Whenuakura River as set out below.</text>
